{"tid":1715702,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"舊T一秒蒙面教學！手足唔好再只係戴口罩","createTime":"2019-11-13T07:03:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T09:04:05.000Z","uid":90601,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4085795405a9dd4747a7d630734bc9cab37fb8a4","tid":1715702,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:03:25.000Z","msg":"人既眼眉同耳仔有好高辨識度 戴口罩仲會被狗咬開<br />\n要全個頭除左眼都包曬佢<br />\n依個做法仲可以方便變裝 一件舊tee就做到 完全唔困難<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://instructables.com/id/ninja-mask-with-t-shirt/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstructables.com%2Fid%2Fninja-mask-with-t-shirt%2F&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLaVm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=8f7bf839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instructables.com/id/ninja-mask-with-t-shirt/</a><br />\n<br />\n我cap埋圖俾你地<br />\n<br />\n1、是但搵件tee 最好仲著得落 因為離場可以變裝 衣料最好夠薄 因為要抖氣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LMrEW2K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLMrEW2K.png&h=f9582ad7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2、套上頭 領口變透氣位<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KmGNmur.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKmGNmur.png&h=dfe039db&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3、衣袖位向後綁 個人經驗係短袖反而好過長袖 因為長袖會條條fing 有機會俾狗咬<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u7UWePu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu7UWePu.png&h=68947e94&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4、拉緊後調整上下 以遮眉為會重點<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wo2Qjf1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWo2Qjf1.png&h=a29f47fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16d1167a2cae352fe20c45088ce3aa2f892fd368","tid":1715702,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:04:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" 